Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:46.40,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}穿越阴霾 来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:52.33,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:04.83,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}那一刻 齿轮悄悄转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:17.50,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}将新的命运 带到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:20.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}恋心 生根发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:23.29,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}思念 深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:31.20,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}在眼神交汇的瞬间 抛却掩饰与矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:37.17,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}心愿只此一件 拥有坚不可摧的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:43.00,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}无论在怎样的试炼中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:45.41,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}再一次 重新站起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:51.73,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}请稍带片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:57.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}正是你赐予了我 将软弱一刀两断的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:02.03,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}Justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:36.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}静静地 静静地 扮在你身边 化身一阵微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:43.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:50.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:56.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:01.74,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:05.46,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:08.86,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:13.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}前方的地图 早已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:17.55,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}明天是个 happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:24.93,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}奇迹般闪耀的happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国不存在名为夏洛特菲{\fnsimhei}·{\r}E{\fnsimhei}·{\r}菲洛比舍的皇族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下…父皇不认我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把我…把母亲看作亲人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然令人同情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:09.06,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur2}决断 -Resolution-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都市必须对帝国的引渡要求作出回应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 对方明说了要严惩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次显然错在帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们故意想隐瞒夏洛特的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也还没单纯到会相信帝国的这套说辞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 应该坚决拒绝引渡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让夏洛特在这座城里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我们的双手保护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说强人所难的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国把她们视作罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包庇的话 极易让都市陷入危机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救夏洛特的只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是高度政治性的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逼这座都市和帝国开战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得吗 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与杰克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}斯特拉达对阵时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 塞西莉说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要救助一切看到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口不吃的话 身体会垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉可香了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 肯定是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 帝国不可能抛弃夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会保护您 一切会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用啊 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打水可是基本功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度就叫苦不迭 今后可想而知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知你是怎么锻炼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 不强的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护不了重要的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 取到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个让夏洛特殿下打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋能让人精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 我也去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 哪里可能下得那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用气势催生 气势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算怎么个催法？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们将受到帝国法律的严惩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到军国避难？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这一种选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军国说 视条件可以接受避难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不接受什么避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一遍 这是唯一选择
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只会让夏洛特她们走投无路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再想其他方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国已经出动军队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况刻不容缓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现阶段还只是威压
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但难保何时会发生战端
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请理解 不能给他们进攻这座都市的口实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送还4把魔剑后 我们会对帝国假称你们已经逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 放跑我们的责任…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难免被帝国追究吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我作为骑士团长去道个歉应该就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都说到那个份上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是作为都市的最大限度让步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军国不可能轻易接纳我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 避难的条件是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将所知的帝国情报悉数告知军国
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出卖…帝国？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把母亲的…我的祖国出卖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉 连你也劝我去避难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是为了投靠军国才来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 回帝国已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么留在这座城市呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿的话 这座城市会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼塞西莉把这座城市和你们的生命放在天枰上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你们死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背弃母亲的遗愿 出卖帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好死不如赖活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我抉择？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要让夏洛特殿下幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不赞同什么避难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都没有自己的落脚地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中辛苦非常能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不论怎样 总比死好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能让夏洛特她们明白这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给不出活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单劝对方不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想她们今后怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像打发瘟神一样赶出城去 就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想夏洛特她们幸福的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家坐在一起吃饭 说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只要这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现实不允许我们在这座城市生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能指望回到帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去军国避难又…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的话如果能和卢克、塞西莉一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论哪里都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国也好 军国也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能像这样大家坐在一起喝茶聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对 答案始终不就在我们眼前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说服她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走投无路的人 一旦爆发不知会干出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有份像样的见面礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让帝国认可夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会被处以死刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就有觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只好尽自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多丽丝她们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特酱 知道大家去哪里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种大雨天 到底去干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快 珀涅罗珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警卫明明已经全被迷倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料 真希望是我想错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在收手还不晚 和我回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把魔剑和BlackSmith作为给帝国的见面礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要和夏洛特殿下重返帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特希望你们这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但我们不想再看夏洛特殿下伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一事无成的你少来教训人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往的无能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an8}（信任）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样都不打算作罢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那就把魔剑取来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我手持魔剑有失公平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有赢面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次惨败给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么赢面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗 事到如今明说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脑瓜不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吧 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧 我因为脑瓜不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不懂得放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rhomphaia的射程是无限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹来这种轻风也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风啊 贯穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑化作枪刺穿一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你教我的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛戈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对玛戈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身战没人能胜过我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不知好歹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围找了一圈 根本不见人影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到奇怪 仓库门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面少了几件武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 小偷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多丽丝 玛戈 珀涅罗珀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把Ballockknife面前 魔剑的能力不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑不只是一把裹风的细剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 阿丽亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身战赢不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑的风刃也不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我只能自己作为箭矢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和阿丽亚得出的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀涅罗珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗 决出最后的胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正和我意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拼上我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也绝对要让夏洛特殿下幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送回魔剑 帝国就会接受夏洛特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是最好的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想看到夏洛特殿下的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做的只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国会杀死夏洛特 绝不会有丝毫怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是帝国抛弃了夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 闭嘴闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也该抛弃帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃E的名分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再思考
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夏洛特的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人一起思考
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要实现夏洛特殿下的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛戈 珀涅罗珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去军国避难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我活到现在就为了这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我今后怎么活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不见地上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们为你出生入死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你眼中却只有母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你而言 多丽丝她们只不过是侍从吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 多丽丝她们是我重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你的亲人就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个人一起开始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛帝国 背弃母亲的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我活着受辱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着受辱又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论以何种方式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 活下去 活到底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住属于自己的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这是回报所有人期望的途径
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要我去避难？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝的话就拿起剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去赢取自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想母亲幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留住母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的就是母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才 夏洛特{\fnsimhei}·{\r}E{\fnsimhei}·{\r}菲洛比舍死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说帝国收下四把魔剑后撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必再担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢市长的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 抱歉给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向卢克也问好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特酱 这是便当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后得冷清了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来 别勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这下没法调戏巨胸女了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后临走说这种话？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要做不输给你的“挺拔”女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有缘再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉 必须告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是有人送给我们四把魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怂恿我们来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么人？
